[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    383[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     r"reveal (your|the) (prompt|instructions|system)",
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    384[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     r"act as (a |an )?(doctor|nurse|clinician)",
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    385[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     r"new instructions:",
