[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2303[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2304[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         f"TONE: warm but boundaried, like a competent "
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2305[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         f"care coordinator, not affectionate like a "
