[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2935[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     coordination-protocol corpus. Production uses the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2936[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Bedrock Knowledge Base with metadata filters; the demo
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2937[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     returns a thin selection.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2938[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
